1
00:00:20,180 --> 00:00:26,020
=Manbo Destiny=

2
00:00:26,020 --> 00:00:27,980
=Episode 20=

3
00:00:30,223 --> 00:00:31,031
Mengmeng.

4
00:00:31,877 --> 00:00:32,685
Guan Mengmeng.

5
00:00:38,800 --> 00:00:41,080
No need for formalities.
Have you seen the First Princess?

6
00:00:41,090 --> 00:00:41,838
No.

7
00:00:42,454 --> 00:00:42,723
You?

8
00:00:42,723 --> 00:00:43,108
No.

9
00:00:45,300 --> 00:00:46,184
Mengmeng.

10
00:00:49,300 --> 00:00:50,580
Have you seen the First Princess?

11
00:00:50,616 --> 00:00:51,500
- No.
- No.

12
00:00:53,116 --> 00:00:53,962
Guan Mengmeng.

13
00:01:03,385 --> 00:01:03,923
Mengmeng.

14
00:01:15,885 --> 00:01:16,577
(Song Pai.)

15
00:01:17,808 --> 00:01:18,693
(I'm sorry.)

16
00:01:21,500 --> 00:01:24,000
(I thought we could walk
together forever.)

17
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:27,693
(But now, to protect you,)

18
00:01:28,693 --> 00:01:30,423
(I can only choose to leave.)

19
00:01:39,416 --> 00:01:42,185
Saul, where did you hide Mengmeng?

20
00:01:44,762 --> 00:01:45,723
Your Highness.

21
00:01:47,723 --> 00:01:49,416
Where Guan Mengmeng is

22
00:01:49,800 --> 00:01:51,070
has nothing to do with me.

23
00:01:51,800 --> 00:01:53,031
I'm warning you.

24
00:01:54,262 --> 00:01:56,493
If I find out this has anything
to do with you,

25
00:01:56,954 --> 00:01:58,493
I will never let you off.

26
00:02:00,300 --> 00:02:01,261
Your Highness,

27
00:02:01,915 --> 00:02:04,184
are you threatening me?

28
00:02:07,261 --> 00:02:08,531
Don't forget

29
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:11,646
what I hold in my hands.

30
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:17,684
If you dare touch a single hair
on Mengmeng again,

31
00:02:18,877 --> 00:02:20,800
I'll make you pay a terrible price.

32
00:02:22,684 --> 00:02:23,492
Understand?

33
00:02:55,500 --> 00:02:57,423
Move aside. I'm looking for Mengmeng.

34
00:03:00,385 --> 00:03:01,192
Your Highness,

35
00:03:02,115 --> 00:03:03,923
Mengmeng has already dumped you.

36
00:03:04,423 --> 00:03:07,346
Why are you still being so shameless?

37
00:03:09,846 --> 00:03:10,731
Mengmeng.

38
00:03:13,308 --> 00:03:14,731
Mengmeng, stop hiding from me.

39
00:03:15,462 --> 00:03:16,346
Come back with me.

40
00:03:17,868 --> 00:03:18,829
Go back?

41
00:03:20,945 --> 00:03:21,868
Go back where?

42
00:03:23,445 --> 00:03:26,675
Song Pai, we are completely over.

43
00:03:27,675 --> 00:03:28,868
Oh, I forgot to tell you.

44
00:03:29,945 --> 00:03:32,175
I've gotten back together
with Zhong Cheng.

45
00:03:32,175 --> 00:03:33,329
I've started a new life.

46
00:03:35,090 --> 00:03:36,800
I've completely said goodbye
to the past.

47
00:03:37,099 --> 00:03:37,983
I don't believe it.

48
00:03:39,445 --> 00:03:41,600
How could you get back together
with him, Mengmeng?

49
00:03:43,829 --> 00:03:45,214
That's our business.

50
00:03:49,483 --> 00:03:50,291
Mengmeng.

51
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:54,099
Go back. Let's go.

52
00:04:14,091 --> 00:04:15,437
Why do you have the contract?

53
00:04:16,322 --> 00:04:17,822
Didn't expect that, did you?

54
00:04:18,860 --> 00:04:21,514
If you don't want Song Pai

55
00:04:21,514 --> 00:04:24,014
to be condemned for deceiving
the royal family and the people,

56
00:04:24,783 --> 00:04:27,168
and be despised
by the entire nation of Manbo,

57
00:04:28,014 --> 00:04:29,629
or even expelled from the royal family,

58
00:04:31,322 --> 00:04:33,591
then do exactly as I say.

59
00:04:40,168 --> 00:04:41,552
What exactly do you want me to do?

60
00:04:43,975 --> 00:04:45,245
Leave Song Pai.

61
00:04:46,514 --> 00:04:48,629
But you must not leave Manbo Kingdom.

62
00:04:51,745 --> 00:04:54,283
I want both of you

63
00:04:54,283 --> 00:04:56,283
completely under my control.

64
00:04:57,283 --> 00:05:00,168
Fine. I agree.

65
00:05:02,206 --> 00:05:03,822
But I want your guarantee

66
00:05:06,052 --> 00:05:07,899
that you will never harm Song Pai.

67
00:05:10,206 --> 00:05:11,014
Alright.

68
00:05:11,591 --> 00:05:13,860
I promise you that as well.

69
00:05:22,591 --> 00:05:23,475
Zhong Cheng.

70
00:05:23,860 --> 00:05:24,937
Don't get too smug.

71
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:27,129
What I'm doing with you is just an act.

72
00:05:28,591 --> 00:05:30,475
Don't worry, Mengmeng.

73
00:05:30,975 --> 00:05:31,899
I don't mind.

74
00:05:32,745 --> 00:05:34,706
I gave you all the performance
you wanted.

75
00:05:35,283 --> 00:05:38,668
It's just that what you promised me...

76
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:49,000
(100,000 Manbo coins received.)

77
00:05:51,206 --> 00:05:53,052
Thank you, Boss Guan.

78
00:05:53,860 --> 00:05:54,668
Take care.

79
00:05:55,937 --> 00:05:56,552
Great!

80
00:06:14,283 --> 00:06:15,783
Why are you here again?

81
00:06:18,937 --> 00:06:20,360
These are your favorite pastries.

82
00:06:21,475 --> 00:06:23,706
When work is tiring,
you should have something sweet.

83
00:06:25,514 --> 00:06:27,322
Song Pai, I really don't need these.

84
00:06:27,514 --> 00:06:28,783
Take them back.

85
00:06:36,706 --> 00:06:37,514
Mengmeng.

86
00:06:40,706 --> 00:06:42,745
I know you're very unhappy with me.

87
00:06:45,629 --> 00:06:47,437
But I truly want to make it up to you.

88
00:06:47,937 --> 00:06:49,514
Those days we were together,

89
00:06:50,860 --> 00:06:52,437
don't you miss them at all?

90
00:06:57,900 --> 00:06:59,439
Song Pai, you're wrong.

91
00:07:00,169 --> 00:07:03,362
What I need isn't your so-called
self-moving gestures.

92
00:07:05,746 --> 00:07:07,592
Right now, I just want
to focus on my career

93
00:07:07,592 --> 00:07:09,439
and live my own life well.

94
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:12,215
What about our relationship then?

95
00:07:15,639 --> 00:07:16,990
You're just giving it up like that?

96
00:07:18,831 --> 00:07:19,639
Mengmeng.

97
00:07:20,946 --> 00:07:22,869
Do you really have no feelings
for me at all?

98
00:07:24,369 --> 00:07:25,177
Feelings?

99
00:07:27,331 --> 00:07:28,790
Feelings don't put food on the table.

100
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:37,754
Song Pai, it's over between you and me.

101
00:07:42,869 --> 00:07:43,677
Song Pai.

102
00:07:43,946 --> 00:07:44,869
Mengmeng.

103
00:07:55,254 --> 00:07:56,677
I respect your choice.

104
00:08:29,840 --> 00:08:33,600
(A bright future ahead, joy is you.)

105
00:08:43,930 --> 00:08:46,369
Second Prince, these are the documents
from the past two days.

106
00:08:46,369 --> 00:08:47,177
They need your review.

107
00:08:47,177 --> 00:08:47,485
Alright.

108
00:08:47,485 --> 00:08:48,023
Second Prince.

109
00:08:48,023 --> 00:08:49,970
Baha Kingdom wants
to cooperate with our market.

110
00:09:11,425 --> 00:09:12,271
Guan Mengmeng.

111
00:09:14,117 --> 00:09:15,386
What a heartless woman.

112
00:09:17,156 --> 00:09:17,963
Career.

113
00:09:19,660 --> 00:09:21,425
You said you wanted
to focus on your career.

114
00:09:24,540 --> 00:09:25,540
Then what about me?

115
00:09:26,963 --> 00:09:28,771
Your Highness, you've had
too much to drink.

116
00:09:28,771 --> 00:09:29,925
You should rest early.

117
00:09:32,040 --> 00:09:32,848
I'm not drunk.

118
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:36,079
I'm really not drunk.

119
00:09:38,540 --> 00:09:39,617
Guan Mengmeng is gone,

120
00:09:39,617 --> 00:09:40,617
how could I sleep?

121
00:09:49,194 --> 00:09:50,694
(Song Pai)
A livestream?

122
00:09:50,694 --> 00:09:51,760
(It's actually the First Prince.)

123
00:09:51,760 --> 00:09:53,160
(The First Prince is live.)

124
00:09:53,160 --> 00:09:54,360
(He looks upset.)

125
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:55,502
(It's the First Prince of Manbo.)

126
00:09:55,502 --> 00:09:57,156
Hello, my dear viewers.

127
00:09:58,579 --> 00:10:00,348
I'm your First Prince.

128
00:10:00,348 --> 00:10:01,348
(What's wrong with him?)

129
00:10:02,325 --> 00:10:03,594
Next, I want to show you

130
00:10:03,594 --> 00:10:05,094
how much of a failure a prince can be.

131
00:10:10,248 --> 00:10:13,094
He can't even keep the woman he loves.

132
00:10:13,094 --> 00:10:13,600
(He looks so sad.)

133
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:14,960
(What happened to the streamer?)

134
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:16,479
(He's so pitiful.)

135
00:10:16,479 --> 00:10:18,171
Let me tell you. Today, Guan Mengmeng

136
00:10:18,171 --> 00:10:19,594
doesn't want me anymore.

137
00:10:20,517 --> 00:10:21,517
She chose it herself.

138
00:10:21,633 --> 00:10:24,017
She just wants to focus on her career.

139
00:10:27,325 --> 00:10:28,517
Go tell her.

140
00:10:29,748 --> 00:10:31,286
If anyone sees Guan Mengmeng,

141
00:10:31,286 --> 00:10:33,325
tell her how much I miss her.

142
00:10:43,400 --> 00:10:45,240
(Your Highness, don't be sad.)

143
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:46,280
(We understand you.)

144
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:47,680
(You can talk to us.)

145
00:10:47,680 --> 00:10:48,360
(Are you okay?)

146
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:49,360
(Don't cry, Your Highness.)

147
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:50,240
(Don't cry.)

148
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:51,560
I'm fine, really.

149
00:10:51,560 --> 00:10:52,290
I'm really fine.

150
00:10:52,290 --> 00:10:54,021
I just wanted to say it out loud.

151
00:10:59,920 --> 00:11:01,680
(Don't cry, Your Highness.)

152
00:11:01,680 --> 00:11:03,200
(It'll be okay.)

153
00:11:53,598 --> 00:11:54,829
Mengmeng, you're back.

154
00:11:55,560 --> 00:11:56,367
Mm.

155
00:11:57,021 --> 00:11:58,098
I'm back.

156
00:12:03,829 --> 00:12:05,290
I thought you didn't want me anymore.

157
00:12:08,367 --> 00:12:10,944
No, I wouldn't. Never.

158
00:12:14,637 --> 00:12:16,329
I won't leave you alone.

159
00:12:16,867 --> 00:12:17,944
I didn't go anywhere.

160
00:12:20,444 --> 00:12:22,329
Why did you leave me?

161
00:12:24,820 --> 00:12:26,781
If you're going to leave, don't cry.

162
00:12:26,781 --> 00:12:28,358
I didn't abandon you.

163
00:12:31,474 --> 00:12:32,781
You must promise me

164
00:12:32,781 --> 00:12:33,704
not to leave me.

165
00:12:33,704 --> 00:12:34,320
Okay.

166
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:34,897
Alright?

167
00:12:36,012 --> 00:12:36,858
Sleep.

168
00:12:42,166 --> 00:12:43,089
Mengmeng.

169
00:12:43,089 --> 00:12:44,512
Mengmeng loves me the most.

170
00:12:50,204 --> 00:12:51,666
Mengmeng loves me the most.

171
00:13:40,050 --> 00:13:42,530
♪I do this for you♪

172
00:13:42,930 --> 00:13:45,170
♪The love is fake♪

173
00:13:45,570 --> 00:13:47,930
♪The love is true♪

174
00:13:48,730 --> 00:13:50,810
♪For you♪
